    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows wear and some minor staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been serviced regularly, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price.",
