    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering a seamless power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this specimen is beyond reproach: the rod bearing service is fully documented, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates to ensure long-term structural integrity. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential lock, providing exceptional rear-end traction. The chassis remains taut, with zero bushing deflection and factory-spec damping, preserving the legendary communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution. A turn-key, collector-quality machine for the true driving purist.",
